description: Recently sold: $60,000. Beautiful move-in-ready home w/ large deck and 2 detached garages in Iron Junction. This home sits on nearly an acre in a park-like setting, complete w/several fruit trees, including grape, cherry,& apple. The main floor level features an updated kitchen with oak cabinets, all newer appliances, including a new gas range and a separate electric oven; large living room with maple floors and an electric FP; two BRs with maple floors and lots of closet space; large walk-through bath that includes a jetted tub, washer and electric dryer. The lower level has a separate living area complete with a kitchenette w/electric stove and refrigerator, family room with gas FP, 1 BR, ¾ bath, and large laundry/utility area. Home has been completely renovated over the past 10 years, including a new roof on house and garages, all new windows and doors, central air exchange, central vacuum, and some new wiring. It also features an outdoor auto sprinkler system for the garden. City water & city sewer.
